Phindisile Pretty Xaba-Ntshaba bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa nke a họpụtara na National Assembly of South Africa na ntuli aka 2019 dị ka onye otu African National Congress
Kemgbe ọ ghọrọ onye omeiwu, Xaba-Ntshaba jere ozi na Kọmitii Portfolio na Cooperative Governance na Traditional Affairs.
